(38, 0, 'vi', 42, 3, 1, 3, 0, 'Hỏi về phí quảng cáo?', 'hoi-ve-phi-quang-cao-17052012', '2', '{"fullname":"L\\u00ea Th\\u1ecb Hi\\u1ec1n","phone":"0906244804","email":"thanhlx0204@gmail.com","question":"Chi ph\\u00ed qu\\u1ea3ng c\\u00e1o tr\\u00ean website khoemoingay.com nh\\u01b0 th\\u1ebf n\\u00e0o?","answer":"<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial; font-size: small;\\">V\\u1ec1 &yacute; t\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh, nh\\u1ea1c s\\u0129 Qu\\u1ed1c Trung chia s\\u1ebb, s&aacute;u n\\u0103m tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc, Anh Qu&acirc;n - M\\u1ef9 Linh l&agrave;m tour <em>M\\u1ef9 Linh &rsquo;06<\\/em> th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nh\\u01b0ng l\\u1ed7 t\\u1edbi h&agrave;ng tr\\u0103m tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ed3ng. Khi bi\\u1ebft \\u0111i\\u1ec1u n&agrave;y, anh  \\u0111\\u1eb7t quy\\u1ebft t&acirc;m t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c liveshow cho M\\u1ef9 Linh m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng l\\u1ed7. &ldquo;Nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn &lsquo;<a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2012\\/05\\/tuan-ngoc-khen-my-linh-hat-hay-chua-tung-thay\\/\\">V&agrave; em s\\u1ebd h&aacute;t&hellip;&rsquo;<\\/a>,  ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c v\\u1eabn kh&ocirc;ng ph\\u1ea3i t&ocirc;i n&ecirc;n t&ocirc;i ngh\\u0129 ra &yacute; t\\u01b0\\u1edfng s\\u1ebd l&agrave;m tour  k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p cho hai diva \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u1eed nghi\\u1ec7m s\\u1ef1 m\\u1edbi m\\u1ebb v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i gi\\u1eefa hai  gi\\u1ecdng h&aacute;t v&agrave; hai phong c&aacute;ch ch\\u01a1i nh\\u1ea1c. Ban nh\\u1ea1c Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110&ocirc;ng c\\u1ee7a t&ocirc;i v&agrave;  ban nh\\u1ea1c Anh Em c\\u1ee7a Anh Qu&acirc;n s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ed1i tho\\u1ea1i v\\u1edbi nhau, mang h\\u1ebft m&aacute;y m&oacute;c ra  nh\\u01b0 \\u1edf trong ph&ograve;ng thu&rdquo; - Qu\\u1ed1c Trung t\\u1ef1 h&agrave;o ti\\u1ebft l\\u1ed9. Anh c\\u0169ng cho bi\\u1ebft,  liveshow s\\u1ebd kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; MC, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; m&uacute;a y\\u1ec3m tr\\u1ee3 m&agrave; s\\u1ebd l&agrave; cu\\u1ed9c tr\\u01b0ng b&agrave;y  nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9 s\\u01b0u t\\u1eadp \\u0111&agrave;n c\\u1ee7a anh v&agrave; Anh Qu&acirc;n. &ldquo;H&ocirc;m qua t&ocirc;i \\u0111&atilde; mua th&ecirc;m hai  c&acirc;y \\u0111&agrave;n. Hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i t&ocirc;i ngh\\u0129 m&igrave;nh \\u0111ang nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111&agrave;n h\\u01a1n Qu&acirc;n&rdquo; - Qu\\u1ed1c Trung  t\\u1ee7m t\\u1ec9m.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial; font-size: small;\\">Liveshow Thanh Lam - M\\u1ef9 Linh l&agrave; ph\\u1ea7n ti\\u1ebfp theo trong series &ldquo;C\\u1ea7m tay m&ugrave;a h&egrave;&rdquo; do Qu\\u1ed1c Trung th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n. <a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2011\\/07\\/uyen-linh-thanh-lam-thang-hoa-cung-am-nhac\\/\\">&ldquo;C\\u1ea7m tay m&ugrave;a h&egrave;&rdquo; 2011<\\/a> v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c gi\\u1ecdng ca Thanh Lam, Uy&ecirc;n Linh, H&agrave; Linh \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ea1i \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u1eb9p  trong l&ograve;ng kh&aacute;n gi\\u1ea3. Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh n\\u0103m nay v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u1ee7a hai gi\\u1ecdng  n\\u1eef h&agrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u1ea9n ch\\u1ee9a nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u1ea5t ng\\u1edd. Nh\\u1eefng ca kh&uacute;c g\\u1eafn li\\u1ec1n v\\u1edbi  Thanh Lam nh\\u01b0 <em>\\u0110\\u1ee3i ch\\u1edd, Gi\\u1ecdt n\\u1eafng b&ecirc;n th\\u1ec1m&hellip;<\\/em> m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ea7n n\\u1eefa \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c vang l&ecirc;n v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 ph\\u1ed1i kh&iacute; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n m\\u1edbi m\\u1ebb. B&ecirc;n c\\u1ea1nh  \\u0111&oacute;, &ldquo;ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111&agrave;n b&agrave; h&aacute;t&rdquo; s\\u1ebd th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n theo phong c&aacute;ch c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ca  kh&uacute;c c\\u1ee7a Anh Qu&acirc;n m&agrave; M\\u1ef9 Linh t\\u1eebng th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111&oacute;: <em>Thi&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng, Ng&agrave;y x\\u01b0a H&agrave; N\\u1ed9i&hellip;<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial; font-size: small;\\">C\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady, ngo&agrave;i vi\\u1ec7c tr&igrave;nh di\\u1ec5n nh\\u1eefng ca kh&uacute;c l&agrave;m n&ecirc;n t&ecirc;n tu\\u1ed5i m&igrave;nh nh\\u01b0 <em>Chuy\\u1ec7n t&igrave;nh, Tr\\u01b0a v\\u1eafng, T&oacute;c ng\\u1eafn, M&ugrave;a \\u0111&ocirc;ng \\u0111&atilde; qua<\\/em>&hellip; do &ocirc;ng x&atilde; s&aacute;ng t&aacute;c, M\\u1ef9 Linh s\\u1ebd th\\u1ed5i l&agrave;n gi&oacute; m\\u1edbi v&agrave;o ca kh&uacute;c ch\\u1ecb ch\\u01b0a t\\u1eebng bi\\u1ec3u di\\u1ec5n tr&ecirc;n s&acirc;n kh\\u1ea5u nh\\u01b0 <em>T&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u \\u1edf l\\u1ea1i<\\/em> c\\u1ee7a Qu\\u1ed1c Trung.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\" style=\\"text-align: justify;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: arial; font-size: small;\\">\\u0110i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n quan tr\\u1ecdng c\\u1ee7a ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh l&agrave; s\\u1ef1 h&ograve;a gi\\u1ecdng c\\u1ee7a M\\u1ef9 Linh v&agrave; Thanh Lam v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng hit: <em>M\\u1ed9t m&igrave;nh, C&oacute; th\\u1ea5y t&ocirc;i tu\\u1ed5i 15, Th&aacute;ng t\\u01b0 v\\u1ec1, M\\u1eb7t tr\\u1eddi &ecirc;m d\\u1ecbu, \\u0110\\u1ed1 t&igrave;nh, Ng&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng m\\u01b0a<\\/em>&hellip; Trong d\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ee7a Qu\\u1ed1c Trung, anh \\u0111\\u1ec3 hai ca s\\u0129 h&aacute;t hai b&agrave;i ti\\u1ebfng Anh l&agrave; <em>Tell him, Woman in love<\\/em> nh\\u01b0ng c\\u1ea3 M\\u1ef9 Linh v&agrave; Thanh Lam \\u0111\\u1ec1u mu\\u1ed1n t\\u1eadp trung to&agrave;n b\\u1ed9 v&agrave;o nh\\u1eefng b&agrave;i  h&aacute;t Vi\\u1ec7t Nam b\\u1edfi theo h\\u1ecd, h&aacute;t ti\\u1ebfng m\\u1eb9 \\u0111\\u1ebb tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i nh\\u1ea5t, d&ugrave; &acirc;m \\u0111&oacute;ng v&