(39, 0, 'vi', 15, 3, 1, 2, 0, 'Làm thế nào để thành công?', 'lam-the-nao-de-thanh-cong-17052012', '2', '{"fullname":"Nguy\\u1ec5n Th\\u00e0nh Nam","phone":"0906244804","email":"thanhlx0204@gmail.com","question":"T\\u00f4i l\\u00e0 doanh nh\\u00e2n tr\\u1ebb l\\u00e0m th\\u1ebf n\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng?","answer":"<p class=\\"Normal\\"><span style=\\"font-size: small;\\">L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa (Andy Lau) k\\u1ebft h&ocirc;n r\\u1ed3i c&oacute; con, nhi\\u1ec1u fan  v\\u1eabn kh&ocirc;ng t\\u1eeb b\\u1ecf gi\\u1ea5c m\\u1ed9ng v\\u1edbi th\\u1ea7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng. M\\u1edbi \\u0111&acirc;y, Ng\\u1ea1o Di\\u1ec5m H\\u1ed3ng (Ao  Yanhong), c&ocirc; g&aacute;i \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb t\\u1ec9nh H\\u1ed3 B\\u1eafc, Trung Qu\\u1ed1c l\\u1ea1i g&acirc;y s&oacute;ng gi&oacute; d\\u01b0 lu\\u1eadn  v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng suy ngh\\u0129 v&agrave; ph&aacute;t ng&ocirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c cho l&agrave; bi\\u1ec3u hi\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a t&acirc;m l&yacute; &ldquo;kh&ocirc;ng  b&igrave;nh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng\\".<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><span style=\\"font-size: small;\\">Di\\u1ec5m H\\u1ed3ng n\\u0103m nay 29 tu\\u1ed5i. C&ocirc; b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u bi\\u1ebft v&agrave; m&ecirc; m\\u1ea9n  L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa n\\u0103m l&ecirc;n 8 l&ecirc;n 9. T\\u1eeb n\\u0103m 1998 (15 tu\\u1ed5i), thi\\u1ebfu n\\u1eef quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh  &ldquo;ch\\u1ec9 y&ecirc;u L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa&rdquo;. V&igrave; mu\\u1ed1n g\\u1eb7p th\\u1ea7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, c&ocirc; n\\u1ea3y ra &yacute; ngh\\u0129 ph\\u1ea3i  b\\u01b0\\u1edbc ch&acirc;n v&agrave;o l&agrave;ng gi\\u1ea3i tr&iacute;. \\u0110i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n \\u1edf n&ocirc;ng th&ocirc;n th\\u1ea5p, nh\\u01b0ng Di\\u1ec5m H\\u1ed3ng  ch\\u01b0a bao gi\\u1edd t\\u1eeb b\\u1ecf &yacute; \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, &aacute;p l\\u1ef1c kinh t\\u1ebf \\u0111&egrave; n\\u1eb7ng  l&ecirc;n gi\\u1ea5c m\\u01a1 th&agrave;nh ng&ocirc;i sao c\\u1ee7a c&ocirc; g&aacute;i. &ldquo;Thu nh\\u1eadp c\\u1ee7a t&ocirc;i ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ee7 thu&ecirc;  ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; m\\u1eafm mu\\u1ed1i. Ti\\u1ec1n Internet, h\\u1ecdc ph&iacute; cho c&aacute;c m&ocirc;n &acirc;m nh\\u1ea1c, v\\u0169 \\u0111\\u1ea1o...  \\u0111&agrave;nh ph\\u1ea3i ch\\u1eaft b&oacute;p t\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng\\", c&ocirc; n&oacute;i.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><span style=\\"font-size: small;\\">N\\u0103m 2005, bi\\u1ebft tin L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa \\u0111&atilde; c&oacute; b\\u1ea1n g&aacute;i, Di\\u1ec5m  H\\u1ed3ng \\u0111au kh\\u1ed5 t&igrave;m \\u0111\\u1ebfn r\\u01b0\\u1ee3u v&agrave; 12 vi&ecirc;n thu\\u1ed1c ng\\u1ee7, may nh\\u1edd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1ea5p c\\u1ee9u m\\u1edbi  tho&aacute;t ch\\u1ebft. Ba n\\u0103m sau, c&ocirc; b&igrave;nh t\\u0129nh h\\u01a1n tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc th&ocirc;ng tin nam di\\u1ec5n vi&ecirc;n  \\u0111&atilde; k\\u1ebft h&ocirc;n: &ldquo;T&ocirc;i b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n m\\u01a1 t\\u01b0\\u1edfng l&agrave;m v\\u1ee3 anh \\u1ea5y n\\u1eefa, nh\\u01b0ng hy  v\\u1ecdng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l&agrave;m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t&igrave;nh, th\\u1eadm ch&iacute; b\\u1ea1n c\\u1ee7a anh \\u1ea5y. T&ocirc;i y&ecirc;u L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa,  n&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng mu\\u1ed1n l&agrave;m t\\u1ed5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn anh v&agrave; gia \\u0111&igrave;nh&rdquo;- c&ocirc; g&aacute;i s\\u1eafp b\\u01b0\\u1edbc sang  tu\\u1ed5i 30 k\\u1ec3 v\\u1edbi b&aacute;o gi\\u1edbi.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><span style=\\"font-size: small;\\">\\u0110\\u1ebfn khi <a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/guong-mat-nghe-sy\\/2012\\/05\\/vo-luu-duc-hoa-sinh-con-gai\\/\\">thi&ecirc;n kim nh&agrave; L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa<\\/a> ra \\u0111\\u1eddi, Di\\u1ec5m H\\u1ed3ng v\\u1eabn ki&ecirc;n nh\\u1eabn: &ldquo;T&ocirc;i nh\\u1edb anh \\u1ea5y mu\\u1ed1n c&oacute; con trai,  nh\\u01b0ng con g&aacute;i c\\u0169ng t\\u1ed1t, t&ocirc;i s\\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng sinh con cho L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa n\\u1ebfu anh \\u1ea5y  mu\\u1ed1n. Chu L\\u1ec7 Thi&ecirc;n qu\\u1ea3 th\\u1eadt c&oacute; ph&uacute;c\\".<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><span style=\\"font-size: small;\\">Ng\\u1ea1o Di\\u1ec5m H\\u1ed3ng c&ograve;n cho ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n bi\\u1ebft, c&ocirc; v\\u1eabn c&ograve;n l&agrave;  con g&aacute;i v&agrave; ch\\u1ec9 nguy\\u1ec7n &ldquo;d&agrave;nh cho duy nh\\u1ea5t L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa&rdquo;. &ldquo;T&ocirc;i \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u1ee3i 20  n\\u0103m, d&ugrave; c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ee3i th&ecirc;m 20, 40 n\\u0103m n\\u1eefa t&ocirc;i v\\u1eabn b\\u1eb1ng l&ograve;ng&rdquo;, c&ocirc; n&oacute;i. V&igrave; qu&aacute;  \\u0111am m&ecirc; t&agrave;i t\\u1eed, Di\\u1ec5m H\\u1ed3ng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n kh&ocirc;ng th\\u1ec3 ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111&agrave;n  &ocirc;ng n&agrave;o kh&aacute;c. N\\u0103m 2011, tham gia m\\u1ed9t ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh truy\\u1ec1n h&igrave;nh \\u1edf Giang  T&ocirc;, c&ocirc; cho bi\\u1ebft &ldquo;nguy\\u1ec7n v\\u1ecdng c\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u1eddi t&ocirc;i l&agrave; g\\u1eb7p v&agrave; l&agrave;m v\\u1ee3 L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa&rdquo;.  Trong ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh n&agrave;y, c&ocirc; c&oacute; h&agrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng khi\\u1ebfn kh&aacute;n gi\\u1ea3 kh&oacute; hi\\u1ec3u: kh&ocirc;ng  cho nam d\\u1eabn ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr&igrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v&agrave;o tay.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><span style=\\"font-size: small;\\">Ng\\u1ea1o Di\\u1ec5m H\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c coi l&agrave; <a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2007\\/03\\/3b9f4850\\/\\">D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng L\\u1ec7 Quy&ecirc;n<\\/a> th\\u1ee9 hai. C&ocirc; g&aacute;i qu&ecirc; t\\u1ec9nh Cam T&uacute;c n&agrave;y b\\u1ecf h\\u1ecdc \\u0111i t&igrave;m th\\u1ea7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u1ed7i b\\u1ed1 m\\u1eb9 ph\\u1ea3i b&aacute;n nh&agrave;, th\\u1eadm ch&iacute; <a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2007\\/03\\/3b9f4850\\/\\">b&aacute;n th\\u1eadn<\\/a> \\u0111\\u1ec3 con theo \\u0111u\\u1ed5i gi\\u1ea5c m\\u01a1. N\\u0103m 2007, D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng L\\u1ec7 Quy&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Hong Kong  tham gia m\\u1ed9t bu\\u1ed5i giao l\\u01b0u gi\\u1eefa L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa v&agrave; fan. Nh\\u01b0ng kh&ocirc;ng ch\\u1ecbu  d\\u1eebng l\\u1ea1i \\u1edf \\u0111&oacute;, c&ocirc; c&ograve;n mu\\u1ed1n n&oacute;i chuy\\u1ec7n v\\u1edbi anh. Cha c\\u1ee7a L\\u1ec7 Quy&ecirc;n \\u0111&atilde; <a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2007\\/03\\/3b9f48c1\\/\\">ph\\u1ea3i t\\u1ef1 t\\u1eed<\\/a>, \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ea1i di ch&uacute;c d&agrave;i, y&ecirc;u c\\u1ea7u L\\u01b0u \\u0110\\u1ee9c Hoa \\u0111&aacute;p \\u1ee9ng nguy\\u1ec7n v\\u1ecdng c\\u1ee7a con g&aacute;i &ocirc;ng. Nh\\u01b0ng nam di\\u1ec5n vi&ecirc;n \\u0111&atilde; <a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2007\\/03\\/3b9f48c1\\/\\">t\\u1eeb ch\\u1ed1i<\\/a>.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><span style=\\"font-size: small;\\"><strong>Hu\\u1ec7 Nguy\\u1ec5n<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>","modified":"{\\"1338613214\\":\\"1\\",\\"1338620833\\":\\"1\\",\\"1338622415\\":\\"1\\",\\"1338622562\\":\\"1\\",\\"1338622663\\":\\"1\\",\\"1338622676\\":\\"1\\",\\"1338622728\\":\\"1\\",\\"1338623063\\":\\"1\\",\\"1339055941\\":\\"1\\",\\"1339118895\\":null,\\"1339119292\\":null,\\"1339131549\\":\\"1\\"}","metadesc":"T\\u00f4i l\\u00e0 doanh nh\\u00e2n tr\\u1ebb l\\u00e0m th\\u1ebf n\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng?"}', 0, 1337233387, 9),
