\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng loa. \\"Truy\\u1ec1n  h&igrave;nh Trung Qu\\u1ed1c c\\u1ed1 t&igrave;nh d&agrave;n d\\u1ef1ng, v\\u1edbi l\\u1eddi b&igrave;nh khi&ecirc;u kh&iacute;ch nh\\u1eb1m c\\u1ed1 kh\\u1eb3ng  \\u0111\\u1ecbnh t&iacute;nh ch&iacute;nh danh c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecd \\u1edf Bi\\u1ec3n \\u0110&ocirc;ng\\", ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi vi\\u1ebft b&igrave;nh lu\\u1eadn.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">B&agrave;i vi\\u1ebft c\\u0169ng k&ecirc;u g\\u1ecdi k&ecirc;u g\\u1ecdi m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b&igrave;nh t\\u0129nh \\u0111\\u1ec3  l\\u1eafng nghe l\\u1ea1i l\\u1eddi c\\u1ee7a l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u1ea3nh s&aacute;t bi\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam c\\u1ea3nh b&aacute;o t&agrave;u  Trung Qu\\u1ed1c trong clip: \\"\\u0110&acirc;y la\\u0300 ta\\u0300u ca\\u0309nh sa\\u0301t bi&ecirc;\\u0309n Vi&ecirc;\\u0323t Nam s&ocirc;\\u0301  5012. Ca\\u0301c vi\\u0323 \\u0111a\\u0303 va\\u0300o vu\\u0300ng bi&ecirc;\\u0309n chu\\u0309 quy&ecirc;\\u0300n cu\\u0309a Vi&ecirc;\\u0323t Nam, \\u0111&ecirc;\\u0300  nghi\\u0323 ru\\u0301t kho\\u0309i khu v\\u01b0\\u0323c na\\u0300y ngay l&acirc;\\u0323p t\\u01b0\\u0301c\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Ch\\u1ec9 sau &iacute;t gi\\u1edd, b&agrave;i vi\\u1ebft n&agrave;y \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chia s\\u1ebb r\\u1ed9ng r&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n m\\u1ea1ng facebook v&agrave; nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h&agrave;ng ch\\u1ee5c comment h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u1ee9ng. Nick <em>Nam Lam<\\/em> vi\\u1ebft: \\"Y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m \\u0111i, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Vi\\u1ec7t Nam ki&ecirc;n c\\u01b0\\u1eddng, th&ocirc;ng minh, \\u0111&acirc;u d\\u1ec5 g&igrave; chao \\u0111\\u1ea3o. Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111o&agrave;n k\\u1ebft, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u m\\u1ecdi th\\u1eed th&aacute;ch\\". C&ograve;n <em>Sanbang <\\/em>th&igrave; hoan ngh&ecirc;nh tinh th\\u1ea7n v&agrave; ch&uacute;c c&aacute;c chi\\u1ebfn s\\u0129 c\\u1ea3nh s&aacute;t bi\\u1ec3n lu&ocirc;n ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 khi nh&igrave;n nh\\