agrave; \\u0111\\u1ec1u kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh v\\u1edbi  v&ugrave;ng bi\\u1ec3n c&aacute;c t&agrave;u xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n. Ngay sau \\u0111&oacute;, CCTV m&ocirc; t\\u1ea3, ca\\u0301c ta\\u0300u ha\\u0309i  gia\\u0301m c\\u1ee7a Trung Qu\\u1ed1c \\"thay \\u0111&ocirc;\\u0309i \\u0111&ocirc;\\u0323i hi\\u0300nh, ca\\u0309 4 ta\\u0300u cu\\u0300ng quay \\u0111&acirc;\\u0300u  h\\u01b0\\u01a1\\u0301ng v&ecirc;\\u0300 ta\\u0300u Vi&ecirc;\\u0323t Nam\\" v&agrave; \\"sau ch\\u01b0\\u0300ng 10 phu\\u0301t, ta\\u0300u Vi&ecirc;\\u0323t Nam gia\\u0309m  t&ocirc;\\u0301c \\u0111&ocirc;\\u0323, ru\\u0301t lui\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<table border=\\"0\\" cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"3\\" width=\\"1\\" align=\\"center\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/Files\\/Subject\\/3b\\/bd\\/90\\/f1\\/hg1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"480\\" height=\\"280\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\"Image\\">\\u0110\\u1ed9i t&agrave;u h\\u1ea3i gi&aacute;m c\\u1ee7a Trung Qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ea1i khu v\\u1ef1c di\\u1ec5n t\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c cho l&agrave; g\\u1ea7n m\\u1ed9t b&atilde;i \\u0111&aacute; ng\\u1ea7m \\u1edf qu\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea3o Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Sa. <em>\\u1ea2nh ch\\u1ee5p t\\u1eeb clip ph&oacute;ng s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ee7a CCTV.<\\/em><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh \\u1ea3nh \\u0111&atilde; b\\u1ecb bi&ecirc;n t\\u1eadp, c\\u1eaft nh\\u1ecf trong  clip, m\\u1ed9t b&agrave;i vi\\u1ebft trong di\\u1ec5n \\u0111&agrave;n Th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 tr\\u1ebb Vi\\u1ec7t Nam n&ecirc;u quan \\u0111i\\u1ec3m,  ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; chuy\\u1ec7n t&agrave;u c\\u1ea3nh s&aacute;t bi\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam b\\u1ecb \\"r\\u01b0\\u1ee3t \\u0111u\\u1ed5i kh\\u1ecfi  Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Sa\\" m&agrave; hai b&ecirc;n ch\\u1ec9 \\"\\u0111\\u1ed1i \\u0111&aacute;p qua l\\u1ea1i\\" b\\u1eb1ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng loa. \\"Truy\\u1ec1n  h&igrave;nh Trung Qu\\u1ed1c c\\u1ed1 t&igrave;nh d&agrave;n d\\u1ef1ng, v\\u1edbi l\\u1eddi b&igrave;nh khi&ecirc;u kh&iacute;ch nh\\u1eb1m c\\u1ed1 kh\\u1eb3ng  \\u0111\\u1ecbnh t&iacute;nh ch&iacute;nh danh c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecd \\u1edf Bi\\u1ec3n \\u0110&ocirc;ng\\", ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi vi\\u1ebft b&igrave;nh lu\\u1eadn.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">B&agrave;i vi\\u1ebft c\\u0169ng k&ecirc;u g\\u1ecdi k&ecirc;u g\\u1ecdi m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b&igrave;nh t\\u0129nh \\u0111\\u1ec3  l\\u1eafng nghe l\\u1ea1i l\\u1eddi c\\u1ee7a l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u1ea3nh s&aacute;t bi\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam c\\u1ea3nh b&aacute;o t&agrave;u  Trung Qu\\u1ed1c trong clip: \\"\\u0110&acirc;y la\\u0300 ta\\u0300u ca\\u0309nh sa\\u0301t bi&ecirc;\\u0309n Vi&ecirc;\\u0323t Nam s&ocirc;\\u0301  5012. Ca\\u0301c vi\\u0323 \\u0111a\\u0303 va\\u0300o vu\\u0300ng bi&ecirc;\\u0309n chu\\u0309 quy&ecirc;\\u0300n cu\\u0309a Vi&ecirc;\\u0323t Nam, \\u0111&ecirc;\\u0300  nghi\\u0323 ru\\u0301t kho\\u0309i khu v\\u01b0\\u0323c na\\u0300y ngay l&acirc;\\u0323p t\\u01b0\\u0301c\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Ch\\u1ec9 sau &iacute;t gi\\u1edd, b&agrave;i vi\\u1ebft n&agrave;y \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chia s\\u1ebb r\\u1ed9ng r&atilde;i tr&ecirc;n m\\u1ea1ng facebook v&agrave; nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h&agrave;ng ch\\u1ee5c comment h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u1ee9ng. Nick <em>Nam Lam<\\/em> vi\\u1ebft: \\"Y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m \\u0111i, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Vi\\u1ec7t Nam ki&ecirc;n c\\u01b0\\u1eddng, th&ocirc;ng minh, \\u0111&acirc;u d\\u1ec5 g&igrave; chao \\u0111\\u1ea3o. Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111o&agrave;n k\\u1ebft, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u m\\u1ecdi th\\u1eed th&aacute;ch\\". C&ograve;n <em>Sanbang <\\/em>th&igrave; hoan ngh&ecirc;nh tinh th\\u1ea7n v&agrave; ch&uacute;c c&aacute;c chi\\u1ebfn s\\u0129 c\\u1ea3nh s&aacute;t bi\\u1ec3n lu&ocirc;n ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 khi nh&igrave;n nh\\u1eadn r&otilde; s\\u1ef1 ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p c\\u1ee7a v\\u1ee5 vi\\u1ec7c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch y\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed1 c&oacute; ph&oacute;ng vi&ecirc;n \\u0111i c&ugrave;ng \\u0111o&agrave;n t&agrave;u h\\u1ea3i  gi&aacute;m, admin c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t trang web kh&aacute;c cho r\\u1eb1ng \\"cu\\u1ed9c tu\\u1ea7n tra (c\\u1ee7a Trung  Qu\\u1ed1c) ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu l&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o d\\u1ef1ng m\\u1ed9t m&agrave;n k\\u1ecbch tr&ecirc;n s&oacute;ng truy\\u1ec1n h&igrave;nh\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">C&ugrave;ng chung ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1, di\\u1ec5n d&agrave;n Nh\\u1eadt k&yacute; y&ecirc;u n\\u01b0\\u1edbc d\\u1eabn l\\u1ea1i  b\\u1ea3n tin c\\u1ee7a CCTV k&egrave;m clip ph&oacute;ng s\\u1ef1. L\\u1eddi k&ecirc;u g\\u1ecdi \\"H&atilde;y nh\\u1ea5n share (chia s\\u1ebb  b&agrave;i vi\\u1ebft) cho b\\u1ea1n b&egrave; \\u0111\\u1ec3 c&ugrave;ng ph\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ed1i h&agrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng phi ph&aacute;p c\\u1ee7a Trung  Qu\\u1ed1c\\" \\u0111&atilde; nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u1ee9ng c\\u1ee7a h&agrave;ng tr\\u0103m th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u1eefng \\"c&aacute;i \\u0111\\u1ea7u n&oacute;ng\\" c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ebb khi c&oacute;  nh\\u1eefng l\\u1eddi l\\u1ebd b\\u1ed9t ph&aacute;t, thi\\u1ebfu k&igrave;m ch\\u1ebf m\\u1ed9t th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n m\\u1ea1ng facebook  chia s\\u1ebb: \\"Mong c&aacute;c b\\u1ea1n b&igrave;nh t\\u0129nh suy x&eacute;t. D&ugrave; tr&ecirc;n bi\\u1ec3n hay tr&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ea5t  li\\u1ec1n, c&aacute;c chi\\u1ebfn s\\u0129 c\\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng ta lu&ocirc;n s\\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n thi&ecirc;ng  li&ecirc;ng c\\u1ee7a T\\u1ed5 qu\\u1ed1c\\".<\\/p>\\r\\n<table border=\\"0\\" cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"3\\" width=\\"1\\" align=\\"center\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/Files\\/Subject\\/3b\\/bd\\/90\\/f1\\/csb1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"480\\" height=\\"242\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\"Image\\">T&agrave;u c\\u1ea3nh s&aacute;t bi\\u1ec3n 5012, con t&agrave;u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1ebfn trong ph&oacute;ng s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ee7a CCTV. <em>\\u1ea2nh ch\\u1ee5p t\\u1eeb clip.<\\/em><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">C&aacute;c di\\u1ec5n \\u0111&agrave;n n&agrave;y c&ugrave;ng h&agrave;ng lo\\u1ea1t trang m\\u1ea1ng kh&aacute;c c\\u0169ng nhanh ch&oacute;ng d\\u1eabn l\\u1ea1i tin c\\u1ee7a TTXVN b&aacute;c b\\u1ecf th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n b&aacute;o ch&iacute; Trung Qu\\u1ed1c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Theo b\\u1ea3n tin ph&aacute;t \\u0111i t\\u1ed1i 4\\/7 c\\u1ee7a TTXVN, Vi\\u1ec7t Nam b&aacute;c  b\\u1ecf th&ocirc;ng tin t&agrave;u H\\u1ea3i gi&aacute;m Trung Qu\\u1ed1c &ldquo;ch\\u1eb7n \\u0111u\\u1ed5i&rdquo; t&agrave;u c&ocirc;ng v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t  Nam t\\u1ea1i khu v\\u1ef1c qu\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea3o Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Sa. Khi ph&aacute;t hi\\u1ec7n c&aacute;c t&agrave;u H\\u1ea3i gi&aacute;m c\\u1ee7a  Trung Qu\\u1ed1c x&acirc;m ph\\u1ea1m ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, c&aacute;c l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng c\\u1ee7a  Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111&atilde; th\\u1ef1c thi nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, y&ecirc;u c\\u1ea7u t&agrave;u  Trung Qu\\u1ed1c r\\u1eddi kh\\u1ecfi khu v\\u1ef1c qu\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea3o Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Sa - n\\u01a1i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7  c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf ph&aacute;p l&yacute; v&agrave; ch\\u1ee9ng c\\u1ee9 l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">TTXVN kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh, vi\\u1ec7c t&agrave;u H\\u1ea3i gi&aacute;m Trung Qu\\u1ed1c ti\\u1ebfn  h&agrave;nh c&aacute;i g\\u1ecdi l&agrave; &ldquo;ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tu\\u1ea7n tra&rdquo; t\\u1ea1i khu v\\u1ef1c qu\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea3o Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Sa l&agrave;  h&agrave;nh vi x&acirc;m ph\\u1ea1m nghi&ecirc;m tr\\u1ecdng ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, kh&ocirc;ng ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi  tinh th\\u1ea7n Tuy&ecirc;n b\\u1ed1 v\\u1ec1 \\u1ee9ng x\\u1eed c\\u1ee7a c&aacute;c b&ecirc;n \\u1edf Bi\\u1ec3n \\u0110&ocirc;ng (DOC), g&acirc;y ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p  t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh \\u1edf bi\\u1ec3n \\u0110&ocirc;ng, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; l\\u1ee3i cho h&ograve;a b&igrave;nh, \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh \\u1edf khu v\\u1ef1c.  \\"Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i ki&ecirc;n quy\\u1ebft ph\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1ed1i v&agrave; y&ecirc;u c\\u1ea7u Trung Qu\\u1ed1c ch\\u1ea5m d\\u1ee9t ngay c&aacute;c  ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng sai tr&aacute;i n&oacute;i tr&ecirc;n, tu&acirc;n th\\u1ee7 DOC, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng l&agrave;m  ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh \\u1edf bi\\u1ec3n \\u0110&ocirc;ng\\", <em>TTXVN<\\/em> nh\\u1ea5n m\\u1ea1nh.<\\/p>","introtext":"Th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u1ec1 b\\u1ed1n t\\u00e0u h\\u1ea3i gi\\u00e1m c\\u1ee7a Trung Qu\\u1ed1c ti\\u1ebfn h\\u00e0nh ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tu\\u1ea7n tra t\\u1ea1i khu v\\u1ef1c qu\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea3o Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng Sa v\\u00e0 ng\\u0103n ch\\u1eb7n t\\u00e0u c\\u1ea3nh s\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 3\\/7 tr\\u00ean k\\u00eanh truy\\u1ec1n h\\u00ecnh trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng Trung Qu\\u1ed1c (CCTV) v\\u00e0 lan truy\\u1ec1n tr\\u00ean m\\u1ea1ng ng\\u00e0y 4\\/7. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ebfn khi trang m\\u1ea1ng BBC ti\\u1ebfng Vi\\u1ec7t d\\u1eabn l\\u1ea1i b\\u1ea3n tin c\\u1ee7a CCTV v\\u1edbi d\\u00f2ng t\\u00edt \\"T\\u00e0u Vi\\u1ec7t Nam b\\u1ecb Trung Qu\\u1ed1c r\\u01b0\\u1ee3t \\u0111u\\u1ed5i tr\\u00ean bi\\u1ec3n\\", v\\u1ee5 vi\\u1ec7