\r\\n&lt;td class=&quot;Image&quot;&gt;Katie tr\\u1ebb trung r\\u1ea1ng r\\u1ee1 khi m\\u1edbi y&amp;ecirc;u Tom v&amp;agrave; t&amp;agrave;n t\\u1ea1, m\\u1ec7t m\\u1ecfi sau 5 n\\u0103m l&amp;agrave;m v\\u1ee3 anh.&lt;\\/td&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/tr&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/tbody&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/table&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p class=&quot;Normal&quot;&gt;Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, c\\u0169ng theo &lt;em&gt;Huffingtonpost,&lt;\\/em&gt; s\\u1ef1 th\\u1eadt kh&amp;ocirc;ng ho&amp;agrave;n to&amp;agrave;n nh\\u01b0 th\\u1ebf. Tony Ortega - t\\u1ed5ng bi&amp;ecirc;n t\\u1eadp t\\u1edd &lt;em&gt;Village Voice&lt;\\/em&gt; - \\u0111&amp;atilde; g\\u1eedi m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ee9c email cho trang tin n&amp;agrave;y \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1ea3i th&amp;iacute;ch r&amp;otilde;. Ortega cho  bi\\u1ebft: &quot;Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi Katie Holmes \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ecdn, m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 c&amp;ocirc; g&amp;aacute;i tr\\u1ebb \\u0111&amp;atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh&amp;agrave;  th\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ea1o Scientology g\\u1ecdi \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ec3 xem li\\u1ec7u h\\u1ecd c&amp;oacute; ph&amp;ugrave; h\\u1ee3p l&amp;agrave;m v\\u1ee3 Tom hay  kh&amp;ocirc;ng. T\\u1ea5t nhi&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave; h\\u1ecd ph\\u1ea3i k&amp;yacute; h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng im l\\u1eb7ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi h\\u1eb9n h&amp;ograve; v\\u1edbi  Cruise&amp;rdquo;. V&amp;agrave; theo Ortega, \\u0111&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng b&amp;igrave;nh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a nh&amp;agrave; th\\u1edd  Scientology.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p class=&quot;Normal&quot;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Nh&amp;agrave; th\\u1edd r\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea9n th\\u1eadn trong vi\\u1ec7c t&amp;igrave;m v\\u1ee3 m\\u1edbi cho Tom&amp;rdquo;,  Ortega vi\\u1ebft. Ortega l&amp;agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t\\u1eebng c\\u1ea5t c&amp;ocirc;ng nghi&amp;ecirc;n c\\u1ee9u kh&amp;aacute; s&amp;acirc;u v\\u1ec1  Scientology. C&amp;ograve;n theo nh&amp;agrave; ti\\u1ec3u s\\u1eed Andrew Morton, t&amp;aacute;c gi\\u1ea3 cu\\u1ed1n &lt;em&gt;Tom Cruise: