h\\u1ee9 m\\u1ed3i nh\\u1eed  kh&aacute;c. L&uacute;c b\\u1ea5y gi\\u1edd, nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed l&agrave; nh&agrave; s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a phim \\"Mission  Impossible III\\". Scarlett Johansson v&agrave; Katie Holmes \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ee9a h\\u1eb9n c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t  vai trong bom t\\u1ea5n n&agrave;y. Scarlett ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u01b0ng c&ocirc; t\\u1eeb b\\u1ecf ngay  khi Tom &eacute;p c&ocirc; gia nh\\u1eadp Scientology. Katie kh&ocirc;ng nh\\u1eadn vai (sau n&agrave;y thu\\u1ed9c  v\\u1ec1 Michelle Monaghan), nh\\u01b0ng b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u h&ograve; h\\u1eb9n v\\u1edbi Tom - ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m&agrave; c&ocirc; g&aacute;i  ngoan n&agrave;y \\u0111&atilde; th\\u1ea7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng su\\u1ed1t h&agrave;ng n\\u0103m tr\\u1eddi. N\\u0103m 2006, c&ocirc; l\\u1eb7ng l\\u1ebd sinh  Suri v&agrave; tu&acirc;n theo c&aacute;c th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c c\\u1ee7a nh&agrave; th\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c sinh con.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">D&ugrave; th\\u1eeba nh\\u1eadn Tom l&agrave; k\\u1ebb &ldquo;t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n r\\u1ea5t gi\\u1ecfi trong h&ocirc;n  nh&acirc;n\\", Andrew Morton v\\u1eabn cho r\\u1eb1ng, ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u, nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed th\\u1eadt l&ograve;ng y&ecirc;u  Katie. \\u0110&oacute; l&agrave; l&yacute; do khi\\u1ebfn Katie bi\\u1ebft r&otilde; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng \\u01b0a g&igrave; Scientology nh\\u01b0ng  c&ocirc; v\\u1eabn &ldquo;nh\\u1eafm m\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u01b0a ch&acirc;n&rdquo;.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><strong>Huy\\u1ec1n Anh<\\/strong><\\/p>","introtext":"T\\u00e0i t\\u1eed ''\\u0110i\\u1ec7p v\\u1ee5 b\\u1ea5t kh\\u1ea3 thi'' b\\u1ecb nghi ng\\u1edd ''th\\u00edch \\u0111\\u00e0n \\u00f4ng h\\u01a1n ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef'' su\\u1ed1t 20 n\\u0103m nay. Nh\\u01b0 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u1ec7, tin \\u0111\\u1ed3n s\\u1ebd l\\u1eafng xu\\u1ed1ng m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n anh k\\u1ebft h\\u00f4n v\\u00e0 l\\u1ea1i b\\u00f9ng ph\\u00e1t l\\u00ean s