ob Thomas&hellip; Th\\u1ee9 ba l&agrave; Tom c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t th&acirc;n h&igrave;nh qu&aacute; \\u0111\\u1eb9p so  v\\u1edbi tu\\u1ed5i 50. &ldquo;D&ugrave; luy\\u1ec7n t\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ea5y, ''\\u0111&agrave;n &ocirc;ng th\\u1eb3ng'' th\\u01b0\\u1eddng ph&aacute;t t\\u01b0\\u1edbng  b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u1eeb tu\\u1ed5i 35. M\\u1ea5y ai \\u0111&atilde; 50 m&agrave; v\\u1eabn thon g\\u1ecdn nh\\u01b0 Tom. Ngo\\u1ea1i tr\\u1eeb \\u0111&oacute;  l&agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi v\\u1eabn \\u0111ang t&igrave;m ki\\u1ebfm m\\u1ed9t &ldquo;b\\u1ea1n trai ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p&rdquo;, Romero vi\\u1ebft.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Th\\u1ee9 t\\u01b0 v&agrave; th\\u1ee9 n\\u0103m, thi\\u1ebfu thuy\\u1ebft ph\\u1ee5c h\\u01a1n, nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c blogger n&agrave;y \\u0111\\u01b0a ra, c\\u0103n c\\u1ee9 v&agrave;o m\\u1ed9t clip Tom m\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u1ed3 l&oacute;t nh\\u1ea3y sexy (<a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2012\\/07\\/tom-cruise-doi-dien-nghi-van-gay-va-tuyen-vo-bang-tien\\/Page_2.asp\\">xem clip<\\/a>) v&agrave; m\\u1ed9t \\u0111o\\u1ea1n video c\\u1ee7a h&atilde;ng Fox, &aacute;m ch\\u1ec9 Tom c&oacute; quan h\\u1ec7 l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng t&iacute;nh d\\u1ee5c (<a class=\\"Normal\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/gl\\/van-hoa\\/2012\\/07\\/tom-cruise-doi-dien-nghi-van-gay-va-tuyen-vo-bang-tien\\/page_3.asp\\">xem video<\\/a>).<\\/p>\\r\\n<table border=\\"0\\" cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"3\\" width=\\"1\\" align=\\"center\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/Files\\/Subject\\/3b\\/bd\\/91\\/22\\/tomkat4.jpg\\" border=\\"1\\" alt=\\"M\\u1ed9t kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a cha con Tom Cruise - Suri.\\" width=\\"433\\" height=\\"554\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\"Image\\">M\\u1ed9t kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a cha con Tom Cruise - Suri. \\u1ea2nh: <em>Mirror.<\\/em><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Nh&acirc;n d\\u1ecbp n&agrave;y, nhi\\u1ec1u t\\u1edd b&aacute;o c\\u0169ng nh\\u1eafc l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng scandal v\\u1ec1 gi\\u1edbi t&iacute;nh m&agrave; Tom t\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u1ed1i m\\u1eb7t. <strong><span style=\\"color: #3f3f3f;\\">Nh\\u01b0ng nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed lu&ocirc;n gi&agrave;nh chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u1eefng c&aacute;o bu\\u1ed9c anh \\u0111\\u1ed3ng t&iacute;nh.<\\/span><\\/strong> N\\u0103m 2003, anh nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c 10 tri\\u1ec7u USD ti\\u1ec1n b\\u1ed3i th\\u01b0\\u1eddng t\\u1eeb m\\u1ed9t ng&ocirc;i sao  phim sex, sau khi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi n&agrave;y tung tin Tom c&oacute; quan h\\u1ec7 t&igrave;nh d\\u1ee5c v\\u1edbi anh ta.  2 n\\u0103m sau \\u0111&oacute;, Tom kh\\u1edfi ki\\u1ec7n Michael Davis - &ocirc;ng ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ea1p ch&iacute; <em>Bold Magazine<\\/em> - v&agrave; \\u0111&ograve;i b\\u1ed3i th\\u01b0\\u1eddng 100 tri\\u1ec7u USD b\\u1edfi Davis loan tin r\\u1eb1ng, <em>Bold<\\/em> c&oacute; clip gi\\u01b0\\u1eddng chi\\u1ebfu \\u0111\\u1ed3ng t&iacute;nh c\\u1ee7a nam di\\u1ec5n vi&ecirc;n. Chuy\\u1ec7n b\\u1ed3i th\\u01b0\\u1eddng kh&ocirc;ng th\\u1ea5y n&oacute;i \\u0111\\u1ebfn nh\\u01b0ng Davis sau \\u0111&oacute; ph\\u1ea3i kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh tr&ecirc;n<em> People<\\/em> r\\u1eb1ng, Tom &ldquo;ch\\u01b0a bao gi\\u1edd c&oacute; m\\u1ed1i t&igrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed3ng t&iacute;nh ho\\u1eb7c quan h\\u1ec7 t&igrave;nh d\\u1ee5c  \\u0111\\u1ed3ng gi\\u1edbi&rdquo;. Tom c\\u0169ng th\\u1eafng ki\\u1ec7n m\\u1ed9t t\\u1edd b&aacute;o l&aacute; c\\u1ea3i c\\u1ee7a Anh khi t\\u1edd n&agrave;y  kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh, anh c\\u01b0\\u1edbi Nicole Kidman l&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ec3 che gi\\u1ea5u vi\\u1ec7c m&igrave;nh b\\u1ecb gay. N\\u0103m  2010, t\\u1edd <em>National Enquirer<\\/em> \\u0111\\u01b0a tin, Katie Holmes t\\u1eebng r\\u1ea5t s\\u1ed1c  tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc tin \\u0111\\u1ed3n Tom l\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng t&iacute;nh. Nh\\u01b0ng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n c\\u1ee7a Tom cho bi\\u1ebft, nam  di\\u1ec5n vi&ecirc;n \\u0111&atilde; gi\\u1ea3i th&iacute;ch r\\u1ea5t c\\u1eb7n k\\u1ebd v\\u1edbi v\\u1ee3 v&agrave; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c&ocirc; tin t\\u01b0\\u1edfng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Tr&aacute;i ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng tuy&ecirc;n b\\u1ed1 v\\u1ec1 t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u s&eacute;t \\u0111&aacute;nh hay m\\u1ed1i t&igrave;nh l&atilde;ng m\\u1ea1n gi\\u1eefa Tom v&agrave; Katie, t\\u1edd<em> Huffingtonpost<\\/em> cho r\\u1eb1ng, <strong><span style=\\"color: #3f3f3f;\\">Katie ch\\u1ec9 l&agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn trong m\\u1ed9t \\"cu\\u1ed9c tuy\\u1ec3n v\\u1ee3 c&oacute; t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n\\" c\\u1ee7a nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed. <\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">&ldquo;N\\u0103m 2005, 4 n\\u0103m sau khi ly d\\u1ecb Nicole Kidman, Tom  Cruise \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c cho l&agrave; \\u0111&atilde; ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ng&ocirc;i sao tr\\u1ebb Hollywood \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ec1 ngh\\u1ecb  m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ea3n h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h&ocirc;n nh&acirc;n th\\u1eddi h\\u1ea1n 5 n\\u0103m. Trong s\\u1ed1 nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ng\\u1ecf  l\\u1eddi c&oacute; Sofia Vergara, Scarlett Johansson v&agrave; Katie Holmes - ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi sau n&agrave;y  th&agrave;nh v\\u1ee3 th\\u1ee9 ba c\\u1ee7a Tom. K\\u1ebft h&ocirc;n v\\u1edbi Tom, c&ocirc; d&acirc;u s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n s\\u1ef1  nghi\\u1ec7p, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u01b0\\u1edfng h&agrave;ng n&uacute;i ti\\u1ec1n v&agrave; c&ograve;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c boa th&ecirc;m n\\u1ebfu ch\\u1ecbu sinh con  cho nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed&rdquo;, <em>Huffingtonpost<\\/em> vi\\u1ebft.<\\/p>\\r\\n<table border=\\"0\\" cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"3\\" width=\\"1\\" align=\\"center\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/Files\\/Subject\\/3b\\/bd\\/91\\/22\\/tomkat3.jpg\\" border=\\"1\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"495\\" height=\\"334\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\"Image\\">Katie tr\\u1ebb trung r\\u1ea1ng r\\u1ee1 khi m\\u1edbi y&ecirc;u Tom v&agrave; t&agrave;n t\\u1ea1, m\\u1ec7t m\\u1ecfi sau 5 n\\u0103m l&agrave;m v\\u1ee3 anh.<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c\\u0169ng theo <em>Huffingtonpost,<\\/em> s\\u1ef1 th\\u1eadt kh&ocirc;ng ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n nh\\u01b0 th\\u1ebf. Tony Ortega - t\\u1ed5ng bi&ecirc;n t\\u1eadp t\\u1edd <em>Village Voice<\\/em> - \\u0111&atilde; g\\u1eedi m\\u1ed9t b\\u1ee9c email cho trang tin n&agrave;y \\u0111\\u1ec3 gi\\u1ea3i th&iacute;ch r&otilde;. Ortega cho  bi\\u1ebft: \\"Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi Katie Holmes \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ecdn, m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 c&ocirc; g&aacute;i tr\\u1ebb \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh&agrave;  th\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ea1o Scientology g\\u1ecdi \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ec3 xem li\\u1ec7u h\\u1ecd c&oacute; ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p l&agrave;m v\\u1ee3 Tom hay  kh&ocirc;ng. T\\u1ea5t nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; h\\u1ecd ph\\u1ea3i k&yacute; h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ed3ng im l\\u1eb7ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi h\\u1eb9n h&ograve; v\\u1edbi  Cruise&rdquo;. V&agrave; theo Ortega, \\u0111&acirc;y l&agrave; ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng b&igrave;nh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a nh&agrave; th\\u1edd  Scientology.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">&ldquo;Nh&agrave; th\\u1edd r\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea9n th\\u1eadn trong vi\\u1ec7c t&igrave;m v\\u1ee3 m\\u1edbi cho Tom&rdquo;,  Ortega vi\\u1ebft. Ortega l&agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t\\u1eebng c\\u1ea5t c&ocirc;ng nghi&ecirc;n c\\u1ee9u kh&aacute; s&acirc;u v\\u1ec1  Scientology. C&ograve;n theo nh&agrave; ti\\u1ec3u s\\u1eed Andrew Morton, t&aacute;c gi\\u1ea3 cu\\u1ed1n <em>Tom Cruise: An Unauthorized Biography<\\/em>, nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed c&oacute; v\\u1ecb tr&iacute; kh&aacute; cao trong h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng l&atilde;nh \\u0111\\u1ea1o c\\u1ee7a gi&aacute;o ph&aacute;i n&agrave;y.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Morton c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0a ra m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 chi ti\\u1ebft tr&ugrave;ng kh\\u1edbp v\\u1edbi c&aacute;ch gi\\u1ea3i th&iacute;ch c\\u1ee7a Ortega. Trong b&agrave;i vi\\u1ebft m\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u0103ng tr&ecirc;n trang <em>Celebuzz,<\\/em> Morton cho bi\\u1ebft, tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi c\\u01b0\\u1edbi Katie, Tom t\\u1eebng nh\\u1eafm \\u0111\\u1ebfn Sofia Vergara  nh\\u1edd s\\u1ef1 gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u c\\u1ee7a Will Smith - c\\u0169ng l&agrave; t&iacute;n \\u0111\\u1ed3 Scientology. Nh\\u01b0ng n\\u1eef  di\\u1ec5n vi&ecirc;n c\\u1ef1 tuy\\u1ec7t v&agrave; g\\u1ecdi \\u0111&oacute; l&agrave; th\\u1ee9 t&ocirc;n gi&aacute;o &ldquo;ngh\\u1eb9t th\\u1edf v&agrave; gi\\u1ea3 t\\u1ea1o&rdquo;.  Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c\\u1ee7a nh&agrave; th\\u1edd b&igrave;nh lu\\u1eadn r\\u1eb1ng, nh\\u01b0 th\\u1ebf l&agrave; Vergara ch\\u01b0a qua \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c v&ograve;ng  s\\u01a1 tuy\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a Scientology.<\\/p>\\r\\n<table border=\\"0\\" cellspacing=\\"0\\" cellpadding=\\"3\\" width=\\"1\\" align=\\"center\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/vnexpress.net\\/Files\\/Subject\\/3b\\/bd\\/91\\/22\\/tomkat1.jpg\\" border=\\"1\\" alt=\\"Nh&agrave; vi\\u1ebft ti\\u1ec3u s\\u1eed An\\" width=\\"495\\" height=\\"335\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td class=\\"Image\\">Nh&agrave; vi\\u1ebft ti\\u1ec3u s\\u1eed Andrew Morton cho r\\u1eb1ng, th\\u1eddi k\\u1ef3 \\u0111\\u1ea7u, Tom say m&ecirc; Katie th\\u1ef1c s\\u1ef1. \\u1ea2nh: <em>Celes.<\\/em><\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">Nh&agrave; vi\\u1ebft ti\\u1ec3u s\\u1eed n&agrave;y k\\u1ec3 ti\\u1ebfp, v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi kh&aacute;c,  Tom ch\\u1eb3ng c\\u1ea7n d&ugrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ee9c quy\\u1ebfn r\\u0169 c&aacute; nh&acirc;n, b\\u1edfi anh c&oacute; th\\u1ee9 m\\u1ed3i nh\\u1eed  kh&aacute;c. L&uacute;c b\\u1ea5y gi\\u1edd, nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed l&agrave; nh&agrave; s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a phim \\"Mission  Impossible III\\". Scarlett Johansson v&agrave; Katie Holmes \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ee9a h\\u1eb9n c&oacute; m\\u1ed9t  vai trong bom t\\u1ea5n n&agrave;y. Scarlett ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ecdn nh\\u01b0ng c&ocirc; t\\u1eeb b\\u1ecf ngay  khi Tom &eacute;p c&ocirc; gia nh\\u1eadp Scientology. Katie kh&ocirc;ng nh\\u1eadn vai (sau n&agrave;y thu\\u1ed9c  v\\u1ec1 Michelle Monaghan), nh\\u01b0ng b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u h&ograve; h\\u1eb9n v\\u1edbi Tom - ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m&agrave; c&ocirc; g&aacute;i  ngoan n&agrave;y \\u0111&atilde; th\\u1ea7n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng su\\u1ed1t h&agrave;ng n\\u0103m tr\\u1eddi. N\\u0103m 2006, c&ocirc; l\\u1eb7ng l\\u1ebd sinh  Suri v&agrave; tu&acirc;n theo c&aacute;c th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c c\\u1ee7a nh&agrave; th\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c sinh con.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\">D&ugrave; th\\u1eeba nh\\u1eadn Tom l&agrave; k\\u1ebb &ldquo;t&iacute;nh to&aacute;n r\\u1ea5t gi\\u1ecfi trong h&ocirc;n  nh&acirc;n\\", Andrew Morton v\\u1eabn cho r\\u1eb1ng, ban \\u0111\\u1ea7u, nam t&agrave;i t\\u1eed th\\u1eadt l&ograve;ng y&ecirc;u  Katie. \\u0110&oacute; l&agrave; l&yacute; do khi\\u1ebfn Katie bi\\u1ebft r&otilde; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng \\u01b0a g&igrave; Scientology nh\\u01b0ng  c&ocirc; v\\u1eabn &ldquo;nh\\u1eafm m\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u01b0a ch&acirc;n&rdquo;.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"Normal\\"><strong>Huy\\u1ec1n Anh<\\/strong><\\/p>","introtext":"T\\u00e0i t\\u1eed ''\\u0110i\\u1ec7p v\\u1ee5 b\\u1ea5t kh\\u1ea3 thi'' b\\u1ecb nghi ng\\u1edd ''th\\u00edch \\u0111\\u00e0n \\u00f4ng h\\u01a1n ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef'' su\\u1ed1t 20 n\\u0103m nay. Nh\\u01b0 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u1ec7, tin \\u0111\\u1ed3n s\\u1ebd l\\u1eafng xu\\u1ed1ng m\\u1ed7i l\\u1ea7n anh k\\u1ebft h\\u00f4n v\\u00e0 l\\u1ea1i b\\u00f9ng ph\\u00e1t l\\u00ea