(84, 0, 'vi', 59, 15, 1, 1, 0, '“Bẹp ruột ” về quê sau môn thi cuối ', 'bep-ruot--ve-que-sau-mon-thi-cuoi-', '', '{"introimage":"290","list_suggest":"","metadesc":"T\\u1ea1i H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i, 9 r\\u01b0\\u1ee1i s\\u00e1ng ng\\u00e0y 5\\/7, sau khi k\\u1ebft th\\u00fac m\\u00f4n thi h\\u00f3a cu\\u1ed1i c\\u00f9ng c\\u1ee7a k\\u00ec thi tuy\\u1ec3n sinh kh\\u1ed1i A, nhi\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ee5 huynh \\u0111\\u00e3 tay x\\u00e1ch ...","fulltext":"<p>T\\u1ea1i <strong>H&agrave; N\\u1ed9i<\\/strong>, 9 r\\u01b0\\u1ee1i s&aacute;ng ng&agrave;y 5\\/7, sau khi k\\u1ebft th&uacute;c  m&ocirc;n thi h&oacute;a cu\\u1ed1i c&ugrave;ng c\\u1ee7a k&igrave; thi tuy\\u1ec3n sinh kh\\u1ed1i A, nhi\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ee5 huynh \\u0111&atilde;  tay x&aacute;ch n&aacute;ch mang h&agrave;nh l&yacute; \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111&oacute;n con v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc;. Kh&ocirc;ng gi\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 k\\u1ebft th&uacute;c  hai m&ocirc;n thi tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 b&agrave;n t&aacute;n h\\u1ecfi han t\\u1ea1i c\\u1ed5ng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng. Gi\\u1edd \\u0111&acirc;y g&aacute;nh  n\\u1eb7ng chi ph&iacute; \\u0111\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ecf trong nh\\u1eefng ng&agrave;y thi \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc khi\\u1ebfn ai n\\u1ea5y \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u0103ng  th\\u1eb3ng v&agrave; g\\u1ea5p g&aacute;p.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: justify;\\">B\\u1ebfn xe Gi&aacute;p B&aacute;t l&uacute;c 11h \\u0111&atilde; tr\\u1edf n&ecirc;n \\u0111&ocirc;ng  \\u0111&uacute;c. Nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111&atilde; b\\u1eaft xe &ocirc;m ra b\\u1ebfn nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111&agrave;nh ph\\u1ea3i ng\\u1ed3i ch\\u1edd v&igrave; xe n&agrave;o  c\\u0169ng \\u0111&ocirc;ng \\u0111&uacute;c kh&ocirc;ng th\\u1ec3 l&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c. Nh\\u01b0 m\\u1eb9 con ch\\u1ecb Thu (Ho\\u1eb1ng H&oacute;a, Thanh  H&oacute;a) tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi con thi m&ocirc;n cu\\u1ed1i \\u0111&atilde; mang s\\u1eb5n h&agrave;nh l&yacute; ra v\\u1ec1. Ch\\u1ec9 ch\\u1edd con  ra kh\\u1ecfi ph&ograve;ng thi, hai m\\u1eb9 con v\\u1ed9i v&atilde; b\\u1eaft xe v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, ra t\\u1edbi  b\\u1ebfn kh&ocirc;ng th\\u1ec3 chen ch&acirc;n l&ecirc;n n\\u1ed5i, hai m\\u1eb9 con ch\\u1ecb \\u0111&agrave;nh ph\\u1ea3i ng\\u1ed3i t\\u1ea1m t\\u1ea1i  khu v\\u1ef1c ch\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ec3 t&igrave;m xe v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc;.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img class=\\"news-image\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/img-hn.24hstatic.com:8008\\/upload\\/3-2012\\/images\\/2012-07-05\\/1341470877-1A-thanh-tri.jpg\\" alt=\\"&ldquo;B\\u1eb9p ru\\u1ed9t &rdquo; v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc; sau m&ocirc;n thi cu\\u1ed1i, Tin t\\u1ee9c trong ng&agrave;y, thi \\u0111ai hoc 2012, ngay thu 2, mon thi cuoi, mon hoa, mon ly, mon toan, si tu,phu huynh, ve que...\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span><em>K\\u1ebft  th&uacute;c m&ocirc;n thi th\\u1ee9 3, nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tranh th\\u1ee7 ra v\\u1ec1 g&acirc;y ra t\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee5c b\\u1ed9  t\\u1ea1i nhi\\u1ec1u tuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng (\\u1ea2nh ch\\u1ee5p t\\u1ea1i QL 1A - Thanh Tr&igrave;)<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">&nbsp;<img class=\\"news-image\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/img-hn.24hstatic.com:8008\\/upload\\/3-2012\\/images\\/2012-07-05\\/1341468845-1a.jpg\\" alt=\\"&ldquo;B\\u1eb9p ru\\u1ed9t &rdquo; v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc; sau m&ocirc;n thi cu\\u1ed1i, Tin t\\u1ee9c trong ng&agrave;y, thi \\u0111ai hoc 2012, ngay thu 2, mon thi cuoi, mon hoa, mon ly, mon toan, si tu,phu huynh, ve que...\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><em><span>11h, h&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch chen ch&acirc;n \\u0111\\u1ee9ng mua v&eacute; t\\u1ea1i b\\u1ebfn xe Gi&aacute;p B&aacute;t<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img class=\\"news-image\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/img-hn.24hstatic.com:8008\\/upload\\/3-2012\\/images\\/2012-07-05\\/1341468845-2a.jpg\\" alt=\\"&ldquo;B\\u1eb9p ru\\u1ed9t &rdquo; v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc; sau m&ocirc;n thi cu\\u1ed1i, Tin t\\u1ee