\\u1eb9 con v\\u1ed9i v&atilde; b\\u1eaft xe v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, ra t\\u1edbi  b\\u1ebfn kh&ocirc;ng th\\u1ec3 chen ch&acirc;n l&ecirc;n n\\u1ed5i, hai m\\u1eb9 con ch\\u1ecb \\u0111&agrave;nh ph\\u1ea3i ng\\u1ed3i t\\u1ea1m t\\u1ea1i  khu v\\u1ef1c ch\\u1edd \\u0111\\u1ec3 t&igrave;m xe v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc;.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img class=\\"news-image\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/img-hn.24hstatic.com:8008\\/upload\\/3-2012\\/images\\/2012-07-05\\/1341470877-1A-thanh-tri.jpg\\" alt=\\"&ldquo;B\\u1eb9p ru\\u1ed9t &rdquo; v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc; sau m&ocirc;n thi cu\\u1ed1i, Tin t\\u1ee9c trong ng&agrave;y, thi \\u0111ai hoc 2012, ngay thu 2, mon thi cuoi, mon hoa, mon ly, mon toan, si tu,phu huynh, ve que...\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span><em>K\\u1ebft  th&uacute;c m&ocirc;n thi th\\u1ee9 3, nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tranh th\\u1ee7 ra v\\u1ec1 g&acirc;y ra t\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee5c b\\u1ed9  t\\u1ea1i nhi\\u1ec1u tuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng (\\u1ea2nh ch\\u1ee5p t\\u1ea1i QL 1A - Thanh Tr&igrave;)<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">&nbsp;<img class=\\"news-image\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/img-hn.24hstatic.com:8008\\/upload\\/3-2012\\/images\\/2012-07-05\\/1341468845-1a.jpg\\" alt=\\"&ldquo;B\\u1eb9p ru\\u1ed9t &rdquo; v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc; sau m&ocirc;n thi cu\\u1ed1i, Tin t\\u1ee9c trong ng&agrave;y, thi \\u0111ai hoc 2012, ngay thu 2, mon thi cuoi, mon hoa, mon ly, mon toan, si tu,phu huynh, ve que...\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><em><span>11h, h&agrave;nh kh&aacute;ch chen ch&acirc;n \\u0111\\u1ee9ng mua v&eacute; t\\u1ea1i b\\u1ebfn xe Gi&aacute;p B&aacute;t<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><img class=\\"news-image\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/img-hn.24hstatic.com:8008\\/upload\\/3-2012\\/images\\/2012-07-05\\/1341468845-2a.jpg\\" alt=\\"&ldquo;B\\u1eb9p ru\\u1ed9t &rdquo; v\\u1ec1 qu&ecirc; sau m&ocirc;n thi cu\