(92, 0, 'vi', 60, 13, 1, 1, 0, 'Hà Nội nên cảm ơn “ông Tây điều hành giao thông”', 'ha-noi-nen-cam-on-ong-tay-dieu-hanh-giao-thong', '', '{"introimage":"298","list_suggest":"","metadesc":"(VOV) - C\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u vi\\u1ec7c ph\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi b\\u00e0i to\\u00e1n giao th\\u00f4ng th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u00f4, nh\\u01b0ng n\\u00fat th\\u1eaft c\\u1ea7n th\\u00e1o g\\u1ee1 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc ti\\u00ean th\\u00ec \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m\\u00e1ch n\\u01b0\\u1edbc r\\u1ed3i ...","fulltext":"&lt;p&gt;(VOV) - C&amp;oacute; nhi\\u1ec1u vi\\u1ec7c ph\\u1ea3i l&amp;agrave;m \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi b&amp;agrave;i to&amp;aacute;n giao th&amp;ocirc;ng th\\u1ee7 \\u0111&amp;ocirc;, nh\\u01b0ng n&amp;uacute;t th\\u1eaft c\\u1ea7n th&amp;aacute;o g\\u1ee1 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc ti&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;igrave; \\u0111&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi m&amp;aacute;ch n\\u01b0\\u1edbc r\\u1ed3i \\u0111\\u1ea5y&amp;hellip;&lt;br \\/&gt;H&amp;agrave; N\\u1ed9i kh&amp;ocirc;ng th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ed5 ri\\u1ec7t cho h\\u1ea1 t\\u1ea7ng giao th&amp;ocirc;ng b\\u1ea5t c\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c n\\u1eefa, khi m&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i \\u0111&amp;atilde; xu\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng ng\\u0103n ch\\u1eb7n, y&amp;ecirc;u c\\u1ea7u nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t&amp;ugrave;y ti\\u1ec7n chen l\\u1ea5n ph\\u1ea3i \\u0111i \\u0111&amp;uacute;ng l&amp;agrave;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng. Ch&amp;uacute;ng ta ch\\u01b0a t&amp;igrave;m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ed1i tho&amp;aacute;t cho giao th&amp;ocirc;ng c\\u1ee7a th\\u1ee7 \\u0111&amp;ocirc; v&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng t\\u1ef1 nh&amp;igrave;n v&amp;agrave;o &amp;yacute; th\\u1ee9c c\\u1ee7a ch&amp;iacute;nh ch&amp;uacute;ng ta.&lt;br \\/&gt;S\\u1ef1 vi\\u1ec7c x\\u1ea3y ra m\\u1edbi \\u0111&amp;acirc;y \\u1edf m\\u1ed9t ng&amp;atilde; ba trung t&amp;acirc;m th\\u1ee7 \\u0111&amp;ocirc; H&amp;agrave; N\\u1ed9i ng&amp;agrave;n n\\u0103m v\\u0103n hi\\u1ebfn \\u0111&amp;atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Camera VOV giao th&amp;ocirc;ng c\\u1ee7a \\u0110&amp;agrave;i Ti\\u1ebfng n&amp;oacute;i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam ghi l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7. Nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi x\\u1ea5u h\\u1ed5 khi xem nh\\u1eefng c\\u1ea3nh \\u1ea5y.&lt;br \\/&gt;X\\u1ea5u h\\u1ed5 v&amp;igrave; nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi sinh s\\u1ed1ng \\u1edf th\\u1ee7 \\u0111&amp;ocirc; thanh l\\u1ecbch m&amp;agrave; qu&amp;aacute; thi\\u1ebfu v\\u0103n h&amp;oacute;a khi tham gia giao th&amp;ocirc;ng. X\\u1ea5u h\\u1ed5 v&amp;igrave; \\u0111&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; c&amp;ocirc;ng vi\\u1ec7c c\\u1ee7a m&amp;igrave;nh m&amp;agrave; l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ec3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i b\\u1ee9c x&amp;uacute;c ph\\u1ea3i ra tay. V&amp;agrave;, l\\u1ebd ra c\\u01a1 quan ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng c\\u0169ng n&amp;ecirc;n th\\u1ea5y x\\u1ea5u h\\u1ed5, v&amp;igrave; l&amp;uacute;c \\u1ea5y l&amp;agrave; gi\\u1edd cao \\u0111i\\u1ec3m m&amp;agrave; ch\\u1eb3ng th\\u1ea5y b&amp;oacute;ng d&amp;aacute;ng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi th\\u1ef1c thi c&amp;ocirc;ng v\\u1ee5 n&amp;agrave;o.&lt;br \\/&gt;Nh\\u01b0ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc ti&amp;ecirc;n xin b&amp;agrave;n v\\u1ec1 &amp;yacute; th\\u1ee9c c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng. V\\u0103n h&amp;oacute;a giao th&amp;ocirc;ng l&amp;agrave; bi\\u1ec3u hi\\u1ec7n r&amp;otilde; r&amp;agrave;ng nh\\u1ea5t, tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a &amp;yacute; th\\u1ee9c c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, y&amp;ecirc;u c\\u1ea7u m\\u1ed7i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc h\\u1ebft ph\\u1ea3i t\\u1ef1 gi&amp;aacute;c tu&amp;acirc;n th\\u1ee7 lu\\u1eadt l\\u1ec7. N\\u1ebfu s\\u1ef1 t&amp;ugrave;y ti\\u1ec7n chen l\\u1ea5n, n\\u1ebfu nh\\u1eefng sai l\\u1ec7ch c\\u1ee7a t\\u1eebng c&amp;aacute; nh&amp;acirc;n khi tham gia giao th&amp;ocirc;ng c\\u1ee9 l\\u1eb7p \\u0111i l\\u1eb7p l\\u1ea1i th&amp;igrave; l&amp;acirc;u d\\u1ea7n s\\u1ebd tr\\u1edf th&amp;agrave;nh th&amp;oacute;i quen.&lt;br \\/&gt;&lt;br \\/&gt;Bi\\u1ebft l&amp;agrave; sai, l&amp;agrave; x\\u1ea5u, nh\\u01b0ng v&amp;igrave; s\\u1ed1 \\u0111&amp;ocirc;ng nh\\u01b0 v\\u1eady kh&amp;ocirc;ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ea5n ch\\u1ec9nh k\\u1ecbp th\\u1eddi v&amp;agrave; ki&amp;ecirc;n quy\\u1ebft n&amp;ecirc;n nh\\u1eefng c&amp;aacute;i sai x\\u1ea5u \\u1ea5y c&amp;oacute; t&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;acirc;y nhi\\u1ec5m cao. Nguy h\\u1ea1i nh\\u1ea5t l&amp;agrave; gi\\u1edbi tr\\u1ebb t\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ebf l&amp;agrave; hay, n&amp;ecirc;n ch\\u1eb3ng nh\\u1eefng s\\u1eb5n s&amp;agrave;ng b\\u1eaft ch\\u01b0\\u1edbc m&amp;agrave; c&amp;ograve;n &amp;ldquo;s&amp;aacute;ng t\\u1ea1o&amp;rdquo; th&amp;ecirc;m \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt h\\u01a1n.&lt;br \\/&gt;Xem l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng g&amp;igrave; di\\u1ec5n ra c&amp;oacute; th\\u1ec3 th\\u1ea5y r&amp;otilde; \\u0111i\\u1ec1u n&amp;agrave;y. M\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u1edbn tu\\u1ed5i khi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eafc nh\\u1edf th&amp;igrave; nh\\u1eadn ra sai ph\\u1ea1m n&amp;ecirc;n \\u0111&amp;atilde; quay xe l\\u1ea1i \\u0111i \\u0111&amp;uacute;ng l&amp;agrave;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng. Nh\\u01b0ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;iacute;t b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ebb bi\\u1ebft l&amp;agrave; sai m&amp;agrave; v\\u1eabn c\\u1ed1 t&amp;igrave;nh l&amp;aacute;ch qua \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ea1y, c&amp;ograve;n r\\u1ed3 gas \\u0111\\u1ec3 tho&amp;aacute;t b\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c. C&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;ecirc;m ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng khi m&amp;agrave; xung quanh c&amp;oacute; nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi t&amp;ograve; m&amp;ograve; \\u0111\\u1ee9ng xem v&amp;agrave; b&amp;igrave;nh ph\\u1ea9m v\\u1edbi th&amp;aacute;i \\u0111\\u1ed9 coi vi\\u1ec7c l&amp;agrave;m c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i \\u0111&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;nh \\u0111\\u1ed9ng k&amp;igrave; qu\\u1eb7c.&lt;br \\/&gt;M\\u1ed9t c&amp;ocirc; g&amp;aacute;i tr\\u1ebb h\\u0103ng h&amp;aacute;i c&amp;ugrave;ng ch\\u1eb7n xe nh\\u1eafc nh\\u1edf, nh\\u01b0ng sau \\u0111&amp;oacute; c\\u0169ng th&amp;ocirc;i v&amp;igrave; ch\\u1eb3ng c&amp;oacute; th&amp;ecirc;m ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi n&amp;agrave;o h\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u1ee9ng. Th\\u1ebf m\\u1edbi th\\u1ea5y, &amp;yacute; th\\u1ee9c c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng ch\\u1ec9 c&amp;oacute; th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ec1 cao khi m\\u1ed7i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c&amp;ograve;n ch&amp;uacute;t li&amp;ecirc;m s\\u1ec9, c&amp;ograve;n bi\\u1ebft x\\u1ea5u h\\u1ed5. \\u0110&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; m\\u1ee9c t\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ec3u. \\u1ede m\\u1ee9c cao h\\u01a1n, h\\u1ecd s\\u1ebd bi\\u1ebft c&amp;aacute;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi kh&amp;aacute;c ph\\u1ea3i ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v&amp;igrave; m&amp;igrave;nh. &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br \\/&gt;C\\u0169ng c&amp;oacute; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi n&amp;oacute;i r\\u1eb1ng, v\\u1ecb kh&amp;aacute;ch n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i l&amp;agrave;m vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;di\\u1ec5n&amp;rdquo;, t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1 nh\\u01b0 trong ti\\u1ec3u ph\\u1ea9m &amp;ldquo;camera gi\\u1ea5u k&amp;iacute;n&amp;rdquo; c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t k&amp;ecirc;nh truy\\u1ec1n h&amp;igrave;nh n&amp;agrave;o \\u0111&amp;oacute;. Nh\\u01b0ng c\\u1ee9 cho l&amp;agrave; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i &amp;ldquo;di\\u1ec5n&amp;rdquo; th&amp;igrave; nh\\u1eefng c&amp;ocirc;ng d&amp;acirc;n th\\u1ee7 \\u0111&amp;ocirc; \\u0111i l\\u1ea5n v&amp;agrave;o l&amp;agrave;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3c chi\\u1ec1u v\\u1eabn l&amp;agrave; th\\u1eadt 100%. M\\u1ed7i ch&amp;uacute;ng ta c&amp;oacute; c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y ng\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i \\u1ea5y hay kh&amp;ocirc;ng? &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br \\/&gt;Ch&amp;uacute;ng ta c\\u1ee9 b&amp;agrave;n \\u0111i b&amp;agrave;n l\\u1ea1i m&amp;atilde;i m&amp;agrave; ch\\u01b0a t&amp;igrave;m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l\\u1ed1i tho&amp;aacute;t cho giao th&amp;ocirc;ng c\\u1ee7a th\\u1ee7 \\u0111&amp;ocirc;, b\\u1edfi ch&amp;uacute;ng ta kh&amp;ocirc;ng t\\u1ef1 nh&amp;igrave;n v&amp;agrave;o &amp;yacute; th\\u1ee9c c\\u1ee7a ch&amp;iacute;nh m&amp;igrave;nh. T\\u1ea5t nhi&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; nhi\\u1ec1u vi\\u1ec7c ph\\u1ea3i l&amp;agrave;m, nh\\u01b0ng n&amp;uacute;t th\\u1eaft c\\u1ea7n th&amp;aacute;o g\\u1ee1 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc ti&amp;ecirc;n th&amp;igrave; \\u0111&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1ea1n n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i m&amp;aacute;ch n\\u01b0\\u1edbc cho H&amp;agrave; N\\u1ed9i r\\u1ed3i \\u0111\\u1ea5y!&lt;br \\/&gt;C&amp;ograve;n nh\\u1edb, H&amp;agrave; N\\u1ed9i t\\u1eebng l&amp;agrave;m th&amp;iacute; \\u0111i\\u1ec3m ph&amp;acirc;n l&amp;agrave;n giao th&amp;ocirc;ng nhi\\u1ec1u l\\u1ea7n, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1ea3 t&amp;agrave;i tr\\u1ee3 v&amp;agrave; t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n c\\u1ee7a n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo&amp;agrave;i, n\\u1ebfu t\\u1ed5ng h\\u1ee3p kinh ph&amp;iacute; l\\u1ea1i c\\u0169ng kh&amp;aacute; t\\u1ed1n k&amp;eacute;m, nh\\u01b0ng r\\u1ed3i \\u0111\\u1ec1u &amp;ldquo;\\u0111&amp;aacute;nh tr\\u1ed1ng b\\u1ecf d&amp;ugrave;i&amp;rdquo;. Sau nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ea7n ph&amp;aacute;t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ra qu&amp;acirc;n r\\u1ea7m r\\u1ed9 th&amp;igrave; m\\u1ecdi vi\\u1ec7c ch&amp;igrave;m \\u0111i trong mu&amp;ocirc;n v&amp;agrave;n s\\u1ef1 lo toan kh&amp;aacute;c.&lt;br \\/&gt;V\\u1eady n&amp;ecirc;n, \\u0111&amp;atilde; \\u0111\\u1ebfn l&amp;uacute;c c\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1eb7t l\\u1ea1